{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":999,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":7841,"text":"Thank you very much."},{"time":9038,"text":"I have a few pictures,"},{"time":11000,"text":"and I'll talk a little bit\nabout how I'm able to do what I do."},{"time":15145,"text":"All these houses are built"},{"time":17531,"text":"from between 70 and 80 percent\nrecycled material,"},{"time":20404,"text":"stuff that was headed to the mulcher,\nthe landfill, the burn pile."},{"time":23579,"text":"It was all just gone."},{"time":25000,"text":"This is the first house I built."},{"time":27312,"text":"This double front door here\nwith the three-light transom,"},{"time":30727,"text":"that was headed to the landfill."},{"time":32891,"text":"Have a little turret there."},{"time":34747,"text":"And then these buttons\non the corbels here --"},{"time":38820,"text":"right there --"},{"time":40005,"text":"those are hickory nuts."},{"time":41385,"text":"And these buttons there --"},{"time":43516,"text":"those are chicken eggs."}]},{"cues":[{"time":44867,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":46060,"text":"Of course, first you have breakfast,"},{"time":47845,"text":"and then you fill the shell full\nof Bondo and paint it and nail it up,"},{"time":51784,"text":"and you have an architectural button\nin just a fraction of the time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":55926,"text":"This is a look at the inside."},{"time":58187,"text":"You can see the three-light transom\nthere with the eyebrow windows."},{"time":61476,"text":"Certainly an architectural antique\nheaded to the landfill --"},{"time":64554,"text":"even the lockset\nis probably worth 200 dollars."},{"time":67738,"text":"Everything in the kitchen was salvaged."},{"time":69649,"text":"There's a 1952 O'Keefe &amp; Merritt stove,"},{"time":71670,"text":"if you like to cook -- cool stove."},{"time":74582,"text":"This is going up into the turret."},{"time":76723,"text":"I got that staircase for 20 dollars,"},{"time":79671,"text":"including delivery to my lot."}]},{"cues":[{"time":82000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":84514,"text":"Then, looking up in the turret,"},{"time":86840,"text":"you see there are bulges\nand pokes and sags and so forth."},{"time":90483,"text":"Well, if that ruins your life,"},{"time":92149,"text":"well, then, you shouldn't live there."}]},{"cues":[{"time":94000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":95901,"text":"This is a laundry chute."},{"time":98724,"text":"And this right here is a shoe last --"},{"time":101163,"text":"those are those cast-iron things\nyou see at antique shops."},{"time":104019,"text":"So I had one of those,"},{"time":105332,"text":"so I made some low-tech gadgetry,\nwhere you just stomp on the shoe last,"},{"time":109102,"text":"and then the door flies open\nand you throw your laundry down."},{"time":112000,"text":"And then if you're smart enough,\nit goes on a basket on top of the washer."},{"time":115810,"text":"If not, it goes into the toilet."}]},{"cues":[{"time":118448,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":120521,"text":"This is a bathtub I made,"},{"time":122228,"text":"made out of scrap two-by-four."},{"time":124309,"text":"Started with the rim, and then glued\nand nailed it up into a flat,"},{"time":128567,"text":"corbeled it up and flipped it over,"},{"time":130285,"text":"then did the two profiles on this side."},{"time":132286,"text":"It's a two-person tub."},{"time":134175,"text":"After all, it's not just\na question of hygiene,"},{"time":137142,"text":"but there's a possibility\nof recreation as well."}]},{"cues":[{"time":139658,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":142451,"text":"Then, this faucet here\nis just a piece of Osage orange."},{"time":148342,"text":"It looks a little phallic,"},{"time":149938,"text":"but after all, it's a bathroom."}]},{"cues":[{"time":151663,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":154632,"text":"This is a house based on a Budweiser can."},{"time":156629,"text":"It doesn't look like a can of beer,"},{"time":158345,"text":"but the design take-offs\nare absolutely unmistakable:"},{"time":160873,"text":"the barley hops design\nworked up into the eaves,"},{"time":163229,"text":"then the dentil work comes directly\noff the can's red, white, blue and silver."},{"time":167001,"text":"Then, these corbels going\ndown underneath the eaves"},{"time":169463,"text":"are that little design\nthat comes off the can."},{"time":171665,"text":"I just put a can on a copier\nand kept enlarging it"},{"time":174308,"text":"until I got the size I want."},{"time":175848,"text":"Then, on the can it says,"},{"time":178419,"text":"\"This is the famous Budweiser beer,"},{"time":180150,"text":"we know of no other beer,\nblah, blah, blah.\""},{"time":182232,"text":"So we changed that and put,"},{"time":183549,"text":"\"This is the famous Budweiser house.\nWe don't know of any other house ...\""},{"time":187072,"text":"and so forth and so on."},{"time":188248,"text":"This is a deadbolt."},{"time":189429,"text":"It's a fence from a 1930s shaper,\nwhich is a very angry woodworking machine."},{"time":193195,"text":"And they gave me the fence,\nbut they didn't give me the shaper,"},{"time":196195,"text":"so we made a deadbolt out of it."},{"time":197890,"text":"That'll keep bull elephants\nout, I promise."}]},{"cues":[{"time":200155,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":201184,"text":"And sure enough, we've had\nno problems with bull elephants."}]},{"cues":[{"time":204062,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":205248,"text":"The shower is intended\nto simulate a glass of beer."},{"time":208185,"text":"We've got bubbles going up there,\nthen suds at the top with lumpy tiles."},{"time":211680,"text":"Where do you get lumpy tiles?\nWell, of course, you don't."},{"time":214393,"text":"But I get a lot of toilets, and so you\njust dispatch a toilet with a hammer,"},{"time":218118,"text":"and then you have lumpy tiles."},{"time":220000,"text":"And then the faucet is a beer tap."}]},{"cues":[{"time":223547,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":226297,"text":"Then, this panel of glass\nis the same panel of glass"},{"time":230723,"text":"that occurs in every middle-class\nfront door in America."},{"time":233594,"text":"We're getting tired of it.\nIt's kind of clich√©d now."},{"time":236126,"text":"If you put it in the front door,\nyour design fails."},{"time":239575,"text":"So don't put it in the front door;\nput it somewhere else."},{"time":242325,"text":"It's a pretty panel of glass."},{"time":243875,"text":"But if you put it in the front door,"},{"time":245640,"text":"people say, \"Oh, you're trying\nto be like those guys,"},{"time":248172,"text":"and you didn't make it.\""},{"time":249347,"text":"So don't put it there."},{"time":251179,"text":"Then, another bathroom upstairs."},{"time":253000,"text":"This light up here"},{"time":254261,"text":"is the same light that occurs\nin every middle-class foyer in America."},{"time":258060,"text":"Don't put it in the foyer."},{"time":260000,"text":"Put it in the shower, or in the closet,"},{"time":262761,"text":"but not in the foyer."},{"time":265902,"text":"Then, somebody gave me\na bidet, so it got a bidet."}]},{"cues":[{"time":268612,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":271058,"text":"This little house here,"},{"time":272710,"text":"those branches there are made\nout of Bois d'arc or Osage orange."},{"time":276663,"text":"These pictures will keep scrolling\nas I talk a little bit."}]},{"cues":[{"time":280155,"text":"In order to do what I do,"},{"time":282445,"text":"you have to understand what causes\nwaste in the building industry."},{"time":286224,"text":"Our housing has become a commodity,"},{"time":288881,"text":"and I'll talk a little bit about that."},{"time":291198,"text":"But the first cause of waste\nis probably even buried in our DNA."},{"time":294333,"text":"Human beings have a need\nfor maintaining consistency"},{"time":296825,"text":"of the apperceptive mass."},{"time":298782,"text":"What does that mean?"},{"time":299957,"text":"What it means is,\nfor every perception we have,"},{"time":302263,"text":"it needs to tally\nwith the one like it before,"},{"time":304877,"text":"or we don't have continuity,\nand we become a little bit disoriented."},{"time":308295,"text":"So I can show you an object\nyou've never seen before."},{"time":311000,"text":"Oh, that's a cell phone."},{"time":313376,"text":"But you've never seen this one before."},{"time":316009,"text":"What you're doing"},{"time":317191,"text":"is sizing up the pattern\nof structural features,"},{"time":320215,"text":"and then you go through your databanks:"},{"time":322803,"text":"Cell phone. Oh! That's a cell phone."},{"time":325559,"text":"If I took a bite out of it, you'd go,"},{"time":327665,"text":"\"Wait a second."}]},{"cues":[{"time":329179,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":330358,"text":"\"That's not a cell phone."},{"time":331731,"text":"That's one of those new\nchocolate cell phones.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":334655,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":336393,"text":"You'd have to start a new category,"},{"time":338104,"text":"right between cell phones and chocolate."}]},{"cues":[{"time":340190,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":342025,"text":"That's how we process information."}]},{"cues":[{"time":343715,"text":"You translate that\nto the building industry."},{"time":345871,"text":"If we have a wall of windowpanes\nand one pane is cracked, we go,"},{"time":348925,"text":"\"Oh, dear. That's cracked.\nLet's repair it."},{"time":350974,"text":"Let's take it out and throw it away\nso nobody can use it"},{"time":353634,"text":"and put a new one in.\""},{"time":354818,"text":"Because that's what you do\nwith a cracked pane."},{"time":357064,"text":"Never mind that it doesn't\naffect our lives at all."},{"time":359548,"text":"It only rattles that expected pattern\nand unity of structural features."},{"time":364356,"text":"However, if we took a small hammer,"},{"time":366808,"text":"and we added cracks\nto all the other windows --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":369398,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":371423,"text":"then we have a pattern."},{"time":372661,"text":"Because Gestalt psychology\nemphasizes recognition of pattern"},{"time":375752,"text":"over parts that comprise a pattern."},{"time":377807,"text":"We'll go, \"Ooh, that's nice.\""},{"time":379610,"text":"So, that serves me every day."},{"time":382780,"text":"Repetition creates pattern."},{"time":384550,"text":"If I have 100 of these, 100 of those,"},{"time":386373,"text":"it makes no difference\nwhat these and those are."},{"time":388671,"text":"If I can repeat anything,\nI have the possibility of a pattern,"},{"time":391617,"text":"from hickory nuts and chicken eggs,\nshards of glass, branches."},{"time":394564,"text":"It doesn't make any difference."},{"time":396102,"text":"That causes a lot of waste\nin the building industry."}]},{"cues":[{"time":398654,"text":"The second cause is,"},{"time":399829,"text":"Friedrich Nietzsche, along about 1885,"},{"time":401754,"text":"wrote a book titled\n\"The Birth of Tragedy.\""},{"time":404085,"text":"And in there,"},{"time":405693,"text":"he said cultures tend to swing\nbetween one of two perspectives:"},{"time":408731,"text":"on the one hand,\nwe have an Apollonian perspective,"},{"time":411975,"text":"which is very crisp and premeditated\nand intellectualized"},{"time":415778,"text":"and perfect."},{"time":418481,"text":"On the other end of the spectrum,\nwe have a Dionysian perspective,"},{"time":421717,"text":"which is more given\nto the passions and intuition,"},{"time":424124,"text":"tolerant of organic texture\nand human gesture."},{"time":426927,"text":"So the way the Apollonian personality\ntakes a picture or hangs a picture is,"},{"time":432270,"text":"they'll get out a transit"},{"time":434170,"text":"and a laser level"},{"time":435846,"text":"and a micrometer."},{"time":437550,"text":"\"OK, honey. A thousandth\nof an inch to the left."},{"time":439844,"text":"That's where we want\nthe picture. Right. Perfect!\""},{"time":442251,"text":"Predicated on plumb level,\nsquare and centered."},{"time":444882,"text":"The Dionysian personality\ntakes the picture and goes:"}]},{"cues":[{"time":448780,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":453871,"text":"That's the difference."},{"time":455840,"text":"I feature blemish."},{"time":457625,"text":"I feature organic process."},{"time":459705,"text":"Dead center John Dewey."},{"time":461616,"text":"Apollonian mindset\ncreates mountains of waste."},{"time":465884,"text":"If something isn't perfect,"},{"time":467550,"text":"if it doesn't line up\nwith that premeditated model?"},{"time":470404,"text":"Dumpster."},{"time":471579,"text":"\"Oops. Scratch. Dumpster.\""},{"time":472867,"text":"\"Oops\" this, \"oops\" that.\nLandfill, landfill, landfill."}]},{"cues":[{"time":475518,"text":"The third thing is arguably --"},{"time":478649,"text":"The Industrial Revolution\nstarted in the Renaissance"},{"time":481126,"text":"with the rise of humanism,"},{"time":482404,"text":"then got a little jump start\nalong about the French Revolution."},{"time":485393,"text":"By the middle of the 19th century,\nit's in full flower."},{"time":488045,"text":"And we have dumaflaches and gizmos"},{"time":490676,"text":"and contraptions that will do anything"},{"time":493945,"text":"that we, up to that point,"},{"time":495809,"text":"had to do by hand."},{"time":497584,"text":"So now we have standardized materials."},{"time":499683,"text":"Well, trees don't grow\ntwo inches by four inches,"},{"time":502565,"text":"eight, ten and twelve feet tall."}]},{"cues":[{"time":504271,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":505320,"text":"We create mountains of waste."},{"time":506767,"text":"And they're doing a pretty good job\nthere in the forest,"},{"time":510332,"text":"working all the byproduct\nof their industry --"},{"time":512848,"text":"with OSB and particle board\nand so forth and so on --"},{"time":515634,"text":"but it does no good"},{"time":517453,"text":"to be responsible at the point\nof harvest in the forest"},{"time":520550,"text":"if consumers are wasting the harvest\nat the point of consumption."},{"time":523933,"text":"And that's what's happening."},{"time":525814,"text":"And so if something isn't standard,"},{"time":527550,"text":"\"Oops, dumpster.\" \"Oops\" this.\n\"Oops, warped.\""},{"time":530507,"text":"If you buy a two-by-four\nand it's not straight,"},{"time":532760,"text":"you can take it back."},{"time":534044,"text":"\"Oh, I'm so sorry, sir.\nWe'll get you a straight one.\""},{"time":536679,"text":"Well, I feature all those warped things"},{"time":539995,"text":"because repetition creates pattern,"},{"time":541834,"text":"and it's from a Dionysian perspective."}]},{"cues":[{"time":543863,"text":"The fourth thing"},{"time":545169,"text":"is labor is disproportionately\nmore expensive than materials."},{"time":548919,"text":"Well, that's just a myth."},{"time":550433,"text":"And there's a story:"},{"time":551619,"text":"Jim Tulles, one of the guys I trained --\nI said, \"Jim, it's time now."},{"time":555202,"text":"I got a job for you as a foreman\non a framing crew. Time for you to go.\""},{"time":558641,"text":"\"Dan, I just don't think I'm ready.\""},{"time":560416,"text":"\"Jim, now it's time.\nYou're the down -- oh!\""},{"time":563406,"text":"So we hired on."},{"time":564781,"text":"And he was out there with a tape measure,\ngoing through the trash heap,"},{"time":568282,"text":"looking for header material,\nor the board that goes over a door,"},{"time":571406,"text":"thinking he'd impress his boss --\nthat's how we taught him to do it."},{"time":574651,"text":"The superintendent walked up\nand said, \"What are you doing?\""},{"time":577526,"text":"\"Oh, just looking for header material,\""},{"time":579470,"text":"waiting for that kudos."},{"time":580655,"text":"He said, \"I'm not paying you to go\nthrough the trash. Get back to work.\""},{"time":584137,"text":"And Jim had the wherewithal to say,"},{"time":585869,"text":"\"You know, if you were paying me\n300 dollars an hour,"},{"time":589267,"text":"I can see how you might say that."},{"time":591308,"text":"But right now, I'm saving you\nfive dollars a minute."},{"time":594409,"text":"Do the math.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":595781,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":598129,"text":"\"Good call, Tulles. From now on,\nyou guys hit this pile first.\""},{"time":601367,"text":"And the irony is that he wasn't\nvery good at math."}]},{"cues":[{"time":603866,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":607296,"text":"But once in a while,\nyou get access to the control room,"},{"time":609971,"text":"and then you can\nkind of mess with the dials."},{"time":612104,"text":"And that's what happened there."}]},{"cues":[{"time":614438,"text":"The fifth thing is that maybe,\nafter 2,500 years,"},{"time":616861,"text":"Plato is still having his way with us\nin his notion of perfect forms."},{"time":620203,"text":"He said that we have in our noggin\nthe perfect idea of what we want,"},{"time":624399,"text":"and we force environmental\nresources to accommodate that."},{"time":627400,"text":"So we all have in our head\nthe perfect house,"},{"time":629882,"text":"the American dream, which is a house,"},{"time":632136,"text":"the dream house."},{"time":633747,"text":"The problem is we can't afford it."},{"time":635550,"text":"So we have the American dream look-alike,"},{"time":637550,"text":"which is a mobile home."},{"time":638886,"text":"Now there's a blight on the planet."}]},{"cues":[{"time":641200,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":642478,"text":"It's a chattel mortgage,"},{"time":644222,"text":"just like furniture, just like a car."},{"time":646223,"text":"You write the check,\nand instantly, it depreciates 30 percent."},{"time":649379,"text":"After a year, you can't get insurance\non everything you have in it,"},{"time":652610,"text":"only on 70 percent."},{"time":653905,"text":"Wired with 14-Gauge wire, typically."},{"time":655678,"text":"Nothing wrong with that,"},{"time":656870,"text":"unless you ask it to do\nwhat 12-Gauge wire's supposed to do,"},{"time":659740,"text":"and that's what happens."},{"time":660967,"text":"It out-gasses formaldehyde --"},{"time":662472,"text":"so much so that there is\na federal law in place"},{"time":666637,"text":"to warn new mobile home buyers\nof the formaldehyde atmosphere danger."},{"time":671225,"text":"Are we just being numbingly stupid?"},{"time":673295,"text":"The walls are this thick."},{"time":675126,"text":"The whole thing has\nthe structural value of corn."}]},{"cues":[{"time":678127,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":680034,"text":"\"So ... I thought Palm Harbor\nVillage was over there.\""},{"time":682630,"text":"\"No, no. We had a wind last night."},{"time":684692,"text":"It's gone now.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":686288,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":689550,"text":"Then when they degrade,\nwhat do you do with them?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":692359,"text":"Now, all that --"},{"time":694626,"text":"that Apollonian, Platonic model --"},{"time":697398,"text":"is what the building industry\nis predicated on,"},{"time":699985,"text":"and there are a number of things\nthat exacerbate that."},{"time":702685,"text":"One is that all the professionals,"},{"time":705227,"text":"all the tradesmen, vendors,"},{"time":706918,"text":"inspectors, engineers, architects"},{"time":709320,"text":"all think like this."},{"time":711438,"text":"And then it works its way\nback to the consumer,"},{"time":713668,"text":"who demands the same model."},{"time":715136,"text":"It's a self-fulfilling prophecy.\nWe can't get out of it."},{"time":718271,"text":"Then here come the marketeers\nand the advertisers."},{"time":720871,"text":"\"Woo. Woo-hoo.\""},{"time":723319,"text":"We buy stuff we didn't know we needed."},{"time":726550,"text":"All we have to do\nis look at what one company did"},{"time":729106,"text":"with carbonated prune juice."},{"time":731121,"text":"How disgusting."}]},{"cues":[{"time":732550,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":734366,"text":"But you know what they did?"},{"time":735698,"text":"They hooked a metaphor into it\nand said, \"I drink Dr. Pepper ...\""},{"time":738798,"text":"And pretty soon, we're swilling\nthat stuff by the lake-ful,"},{"time":741816,"text":"by the billions of gallons."},{"time":743551,"text":"It doesn't even have real prunes!\nDoesn't even keep you regular."}]},{"cues":[{"time":746712,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":748496,"text":"My oh my, that makes it worse."},{"time":750550,"text":"And we get sucked\ninto that faster than anything."}]},{"cues":[{"time":753770,"text":"Then, a man named\nJean-Paul Sartre wrote a book"},{"time":756503,"text":"titled \"Being and Nothingness.\""},{"time":758012,"text":"It's a pretty quick read.\nYou can snap through it in maybe --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":760958,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":762046,"text":"maybe two years,"},{"time":763222,"text":"if you read eight hours a day."},{"time":765550,"text":"In there, he talked\nabout the divided self."},{"time":767887,"text":"He said human beings act differently\nwhen they know they're alone"},{"time":770989,"text":"than when they know\nsomebody else is around."},{"time":773073,"text":"So if I'm eating spaghetti,\nand I know I'm alone,"},{"time":775399,"text":"I can eat like a backhoe."},{"time":776891,"text":"I can wipe my mouth on my sleeve,\nnapkin on the table,"},{"time":780129,"text":"chew with my mouth open,\nmake little noises,"},{"time":783470,"text":"scratch wherever I want."}]},{"cues":[{"time":785471,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":787355,"text":"But as soon as you walk in,"},{"time":788826,"text":"I go, \"Oops! Lil' spaghetti sauce there.\""},{"time":791328,"text":"Napkin in my lap, half-bites,"},{"time":793205,"text":"chew with my mouth closed, no scratching."},{"time":795462,"text":"Now, what I'm doing\nis fulfilling your expectations"},{"time":800421,"text":"of how I should live my life."},{"time":803819,"text":"I feel that expectation,"},{"time":805625,"text":"and so I accommodate it,"},{"time":807065,"text":"and I'm living my life according\nto what you expect me to do."},{"time":810335,"text":"That happens in the building\nindustry as well."},{"time":812630,"text":"That's why all subdivisions look the same."},{"time":815509,"text":"Sometimes, we even have\nthese formalized cultural expectations."},{"time":819649,"text":"I'll bet all your shoes match."},{"time":821550,"text":"Sure enough, we all buy into that ..."}]},{"cues":[{"time":823759,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":825433,"text":"And with gated communities,"},{"time":827882,"text":"we have a formalized expectation,"},{"time":830282,"text":"with a homeowners' association."},{"time":831884,"text":"Sometimes those guys are Nazis,"},{"time":833606,"text":"my oh my."},{"time":835930,"text":"That exacerbates and continues this model."}]},{"cues":[{"time":839712,"text":"The last thing is gregariousness."},{"time":842408,"text":"Human beings are a social species."},{"time":844345,"text":"We like to hang together in groups,"},{"time":847067,"text":"just like wildebeests, just like lions."},{"time":848971,"text":"Wildebeests don't hang with lions,"},{"time":850651,"text":"because lions eat wildebeests."},{"time":852690,"text":"Human beings are like that."},{"time":854160,"text":"We do what that group does"},{"time":856280,"text":"that we're trying to identify with."},{"time":858682,"text":"You see this in junior high a lot."},{"time":861291,"text":"Those kids, they'll work\nall summer long -- kill themselves --"},{"time":865686,"text":"so that they can afford\none pair of designer jeans."},{"time":869918,"text":"So along about September,"},{"time":872200,"text":"they can stride in and go,"},{"time":874201,"text":"\"I'm important today. See?\nDon't touch my designer jeans!"},{"time":878439,"text":"I see you don't have designer jeans."},{"time":881300,"text":"You're not one of the beautiful --\nSee, I'm one of the beautiful people."},{"time":885020,"text":"See my jeans?\""},{"time":886232,"text":"Right there is reason\nenough to have uniforms."},{"time":889185,"text":"And so that happens\nin the building industry as well."}]},{"cues":[{"time":892678,"text":"We have confused\nMaslow's hierarchy of needs,"},{"time":896921,"text":"just a little bit."},{"time":898550,"text":"On the bottom tier, we have basic needs:"},{"time":901928,"text":"shelter, clothing, food,\nwater, mating and so forth."},{"time":905486,"text":"Second: security. Third: relationships."},{"time":907848,"text":"Fourth: status, self-esteem --\nthat is, vanity --"},{"time":910890,"text":"and we're taking vanity\nand shoving it down here."},{"time":914343,"text":"And so we end up"},{"time":916827,"text":"with vain decisions,"},{"time":919605,"text":"and we can't even afford our mortgage."},{"time":921821,"text":"We can't afford to eat\nanything except beans;"}]},{"cues":[{"time":924599,"text":"that is, our housing\nhas become a commodity."},{"time":928813,"text":"And it takes a little bit of nerve"},{"time":932123,"text":"to dive into those primal,"},{"time":934550,"text":"terrifying parts of ourselves"},{"time":937550,"text":"and make our own decisions"},{"time":940002,"text":"and not make our housing a commodity,"},{"time":942003,"text":"but make it something\nthat bubbles up from seminal sources."},{"time":945550,"text":"That takes a little bit of nerve,"},{"time":947351,"text":"and, darn it, once in a while, you fail."},{"time":950973,"text":"But that's okay."},{"time":953180,"text":"If failure destroys you,"},{"time":954992,"text":"then you can't do this."},{"time":956246,"text":"I fail all the time, every day,"},{"time":958776,"text":"and I've had some whopping\nfailures, I promise --"},{"time":962512,"text":"big, public, humiliating,\nembarrassing failures."}]},{"cues":[{"time":965550,"text":"Everybody points and laughs,"},{"time":967014,"text":"and they say, \"He tried it a fifth time,\nand it still didn't work!"},{"time":970134,"text":"What a moron!\""},{"time":971538,"text":"Early on, contractors come by and say,"},{"time":973550,"text":"\"Dan, you're a cute little bunny,"},{"time":975337,"text":"but you know,\nthis just isn't going to work."},{"time":977519,"text":"What don't you do this?\nWhy don't you do that?\""},{"time":979874,"text":"And your instinct is to say,"},{"time":982404,"text":"\"Well, why don't you suck an egg?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":984095,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":985550,"text":"But you don't say that,"},{"time":987238,"text":"because they're the guys you're targeting."}]},{"cues":[{"time":990191,"text":"And so what we've done --"},{"time":993194,"text":"and this isn't just in housing;\nit's in clothing and food"},{"time":996611,"text":"and our transportation\nneeds, our energy --"},{"time":999488,"text":"we sprawl just a little bit."},{"time":1002996,"text":"And when I get a little bit of press,"},{"time":1005550,"text":"I hear from people all over the world."},{"time":1007859,"text":"And we may have invented excess,"},{"time":1010702,"text":"but the problem of waste is worldwide."},{"time":1015184,"text":"We're in trouble."},{"time":1018185,"text":"And I don't wear ammo belts\ncrisscrossing my chest"},{"time":1021263,"text":"and a red bandana."},{"time":1023375,"text":"But we're clearly in trouble."},{"time":1025598,"text":"And what we need to do is reconnect"},{"time":1029550,"text":"with those really primal\nparts of ourselves"},{"time":1033211,"text":"and make some decisions and say,"},{"time":1035281,"text":"\"You know, I think I would like to put\nCDs across the wall there."},{"time":1040034,"text":"What do you think, honey?\""},{"time":1042011,"text":"If it doesn't work, take it down."},{"time":1044859,"text":"What we need to do is reconnect\nwith who we really are,"},{"time":1048462,"text":"and that's thrilling indeed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1051483,"text":"Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1052690,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}